{"tid":1152967,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國男團突解散！傳主因有人與30歲女性本部長「長時間維持不正當性關係」","createTime":"2019-05-13T10:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T11:57:00.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"842cd3abf0f2c51c2db65510a83a4a2036eecef8","tid":1152967,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T10:31:13.000Z","msg":"由14位成員組成的韓國男團「14U」2017年出道，至今已出3張單曲，今(13日)媒體驚曝所屬「BG Entertainment」宣布14U將解散，而主因竟是20多歲的成員A和30歲公司女性本部長「長時間維持不正當性關係」，使成員家屬要求解約，公司稍早對此否認，說傳聞太誇張，是因各自志向不同才決定解散。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-05-13/900/20190513002637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-05-13%2F900%2F20190513002637.jpg&h=a8a50dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14U爆出解散是因為有成員和女性高層有性關係。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士透露，今年2月到4月間，14U完成了在日本的20場演唱會後，除了其中的一名成員，其他十三名成員都要求和經紀公司解除合約，而打算離開的成員透露，認主因與公司偏愛其中一位成員有關，因對粉絲十分抱歉，所以無法在第一時間對外說明此事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RBiTdjMsbh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRBiTdjMsbh4&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihC8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=aefe0c7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RBiTdjMsbh4</a><br />\n出道2年的14U另有傳言指有成員跟粉絲也有過性關係。<br />\n<br />\n《Xportsnews》稍早報導，出道2年的14U解散理由其實是成員A和公司女性本部長私下有不正當性關係，被工作人員和成員發現後，A堅稱和本部長是交往中的關係，另有傳言指A跟粉絲也有過性關係，其他成員便要求解約，公司最後決定留下一名成員並解散團體，對此，工作人員回應沒這種事，稱是志願不同，和成員跟其家屬協商後才解散。"},{"pid":"ecc386ed4cbeb4ee2c3c5cb5274b7bab5e2a1d8f","tid":1152967,"uid":165368,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T10:49:51.000Z","msg":"呢個團聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9489783680800e3b228cb014fbf8da6369d8242b","tid":1152967,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"996c7af3fd32e3b5025b7bd3fd1a66985bc1f171","tid":1152967,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"one for you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9420256bc9ee9ad8f42b9fe9f0aa642defea169","tid":1152967,"uid":137470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"公司最後決定<span style=\"color: red;\">留下一名成員</span>並解散團體<br />\n咁咪等於自爆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3e77ff0982157091c610c58c5082a1536f7a30","tid":1152967,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"14k我就識....."},{"pid":"f9605d3e88b632aee8a0b8cf4ee1a1e0df79f55d","tid":1152967,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"正皮畀樓主條片"},{"pid":"0b5d792dae9e2558298f3b206f54abf9644d5928","tid":1152967,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"男團=鴨團<br />\n女團=雞團"}]}